text:
Name: Daniel Nichols.
Graduation Year: 2021.
Description: Daniel Nichols is a dedicated Business Administration student with a strong passion for innovation and learning. Throughout their academic journey, they have gained experience in business administration research and practical applications. They aspire to become a sociologist researching cultural and social behavior. Their dedication to excellence and problem-solving skills make them a promising professional in their field..
